From: Tarun Alle <Tarun.Alle@microchip.com>
Date: Thu, 14 Nov 2024 15:49:51 +0530
Subject: net: phy: microchip_t1: Clause-45 PHY loopback support for LAN887x
Patch-mainline: v6.13-rc1
Git-commit: 025b2bbc5ab1c9ccd50189cae028d1b2bf3d433e
References: jsc#PED-15498

Adds support for clause-45 PHY loopback for the Microchip LAN887x driver.

Signed-off-by: Tarun Alle <Tarun.Alle@microchip.com>
Reviewed-by: Andrew Lunn <andrew@lunn.ch>
Link: https://patch.msgid.link/20241114101951.382996-1-Tarun.Alle@microchip.com
Signed-off-by: Jakub Kicinski <kuba@kernel.org>
Acked-by: Steffen Jaeckel <sjaeckel@suse.de>
---
 drivers/net/phy/microchip_t1.c |    1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

--- a/drivers/net/phy/microchip_t1.c
+++ b/drivers/net/phy/microchip_t1.c
@@ -2113,6 +2113,7 @@ static struct phy_driver microchip_t1_ph
 		.handle_interrupt = lan887x_handle_interrupt,
 		.get_sqi	= lan887x_get_sqi,
 		.get_sqi_max	= lan87xx_get_sqi_max,
+		.set_loopback	= genphy_c45_loopback,
 	}
 };
 
